icitly requires full pipeline validation across sequential stages with at least one real agentic decision (draft generation) plus downstream handoff correctness. Failures can emerge only across the chained sequence (MULTI-STEP/workflow boundary), so lower levels under-cover end-to-end orchestration risk.","test_description":"Run the production-like pipeline on real email-thread fixtures (or live mailbox in a controlled test account): ingest thread, generate with real LLM, execute fact-check stage, surface approval UI/state, and verify no send before approval and coherent artifacts passed between stages.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.04,"System":0.1,"Agentic":0.2,"Workflow":0.65}}]}
